//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Telescope parameters
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Altitude of the balloon in meters

* TELALT 2930

Latitude (Polar) and longitude of telescope

* TELLAT 39
* TELLONG 113

Angle from zenith where the telescope is pointing in degrees

* TELPOINTING 91.56

Collection area of telescope

* TELCOLLECTIONAREA 1

Focal length of optics in mm
* TELFOCALLENGTH 1485

Area simulated enhancement in degrees
* ANGLEINCREASE 0

* ANGLESHOWERINCREASE 0

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Camera parameters
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

* CAMANGULARWIDTH 3.8
* CAMANGULARHEIGHT 3.8
* CAMERAWIDTH 196
* CAMERAHEIGHT 196

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Shower parameters
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Number of showers that will be simulated

* NSHOWERS 100

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Source parameters
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Boolean specifying if below the limb
* ISBELOWLIMB 1

Boolean specifying if it is a point source

* ISPOINTSOURCE 0

Azimuth angle in degrees

* AZIMUTHANGLE 0

Zenith angle for the point source in degrees

* ZENITHANGLE 45

Energy of incoming neutrino in Log(E[GeV])

* NEUTRINOENERGY 10

Energy of incoming cosmic ray in GeV
* COSMICRAYENERGY 1e6

Energy Spectrum Parameters
* ENERGYSPECTRUM 0
* GAMMAINDEX 2.7
* ESAMPLESTRT 1e8
* ESAMPLEEND 1e12

* BSMMEANLIFE 1.0
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
CHASM parameters
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Radius of collection sphere. Sphere should include the whole telescope
collection area in meters.

* COLLECTIONSPHERERADIUS 0.8


